	<div class="entry-author-malcolmgladwell entry-type-post entry" id="entry-6a00d83451c8bb69e20120a6b10b2c970b">
       <div class="entry-inner">
					<h3 class="entry-header"><a href="https://gladwell.typepad.com/gladwellcom/2009/11/letting-igons-be-igons.html">Letting Igons be Igons</a></h3>
		



		<div class="entry-content">

			<div class="entry-body">
				<p><a href="https://gladwell.typepad.com/.a/6a00d83451c8bb69e20120a6b10793970b-pi" style="DISPLAY: inline"><img alt="IMG00052-20091118-1519" border="0" class="asset asset-image at-xid-6a00d83451c8bb69e20120a6b10793970b image-full " src="https://gladwell.typepad.com/.a/6a00d83451c8bb69e20120a6b10793970b-800wi" title="IMG00052-20091118-1519" /></a></p>
<p>&#0160;From &quot;Blowing Up,&quot; by Malcolm Gladwell, The New Yorker, April 22,2002</p>
